npc.name: 学究のタゼル・メイェアン

lines: Squawk! Disturb me, featherless one must not! Hard at work on revolutionary new control mechanism, I am! Go here, this does, and...squawk! Perfection!

Squawk! Many ingenious new developments, I have made! Much help, you have provided. Proved not only a capable craftswomancraftsman, but a friend to Ehcatl, you have. On behalf of all, our gratitude, I offer.

obj.n: ブッ込みイクサル伝説
翼を広げ、何よりも高く
